DP solution is not best for this question but i just want to share my idea
First we creat two dp array, in the right dp ,
If at Index i we have 'L' then dp[i] = 0;
If at Index i we have 'R' then dp[i] = 1;
If at Index i we have '.' then if dp[i - 1] is postive , dp[i] = dp[i - 1] + 1, else dp[i] = 0;
we do the same thing with the left dp
now we have two dp array, so we can get the answer we want.
```
